<i> the nerds and the jocks</i>

04:32.573 --> 04:35.373
<i> Were forced to walk the line</i>
<i> between sports and art,</i>

04:35.442 --> 04:38.076
<i> As if they were walking</i>
<i> a tightrope.</i>

04:38.211 --> 04:39.778
<i> Which, come to think of it,</i>
<i> [players yell]</i>

04:39.780 --> 04:41.747
<i> Is itself both a sport</i>
<i> and an art.</i>

04:41.882 --> 04:44.215
[sticks thwap,
shrill whistle blast]

04:44.285 --> 04:46.451
