09:03.110 --> 09:04.776
- Well, that will give you
more time

09:04.778 --> 09:06.644
To learn a lesson
about humility.

09:08.015 --> 09:10.181
[chair scrapes back]
- so I'm, I'm doing this now?

09:11.251 --> 09:12.784
- Yes.

09:14.154 --> 09:16.721
<i> Adult mark: Humility...</i>
<i> Or humiliation?</i>

09:16.790 --> 09:19.057
[rock music plays]

09:19.059 --> 09:22.193
♪♪♪

09:22.229 --> 09:24.195
