09:32.539 --> 09:34.939
- Better than okay, I hope,
after all that coaching.

09:34.975 --> 09:37.943
So, did you get it - hamar?

09:40.047 --> 09:43.280
- Actually, [sighs] I...

09:45.953 --> 09:47.819
<i> Adult mark: I wanted to be</i>
<i> an actor.</i>

09:47.821 --> 09:50.555
- I'm... Yes, I'm... I'm hamar!

09:50.557 --> 09:52.290
- [excited] hamar! Ha-ha!

09:52.425 --> 09:54.425
<i> Adult mark: And after all,</i>

09:54.494 --> 09:56.694
<i> What is an actor</i>
<i> but a glorified liar?</i>

09:56.829 --> 09:59.430
- Like father, like son!
- Hmm.

09:59.499 --> 10:01.633
<i> Adult mark: If only</i>
<i> sister margaret</i>

10:01.635 --> 10:03.567
<i> Had seen that performance.</i>
<i> [lunchbox thumps]</i>

10:06.840 --> 10:08.239
O: ♪ anything
<i> is possible ♪</i>

10:08.275 --> 10:09.974
