10:13.179 --> 10:14.912
- Mary, look at the way
he carries that plate.

10:14.948 --> 10:16.715
<i> Such authenticity!</i>

10:16.850 --> 10:18.750
I really feel like
I'm in a restaurant.

10:18.885 --> 10:21.385
- Yes, I can see by the way
you expect to be served.

10:21.421 --> 10:23.855
- Do I have to go to this play?
- No!

10:23.990 --> 10:26.224
Uh, the arts aren't
for everyone.

10:26.293 --> 10:28.059
In fact, all o' you can skip it
if you want.

10:28.095 --> 10:30.161
- [snorts softly]
- great!

10:30.296 --> 10:32.196
I'm going to the movies.
- You'll do no such thing!

10:32.265 --> 10:34.265
