in a theatrical production.

10:35.535 --> 10:37.535
- Dad, it's really not
that big a deal.

10:38.605 --> 10:39.937
- It is to me.

10:39.973 --> 10:41.673
We are all gonna go see
that play,

10:41.808 --> 10:43.741
