running footsteps]

10:55.088 --> 10:58.289
[handset clatters]
- good day. Critch residence.

10:58.291 --> 11:01.125
[gasps] elizabeth critch?
- Hey.

11:02.796 --> 11:04.762
- She can't come to the phone.
She's lying down.

11:04.798 --> 11:07.965
One might say...
She's dead to the world.

11:08.035 --> 11:10.501
Oh, I see. Yes.

11:12.272 --> 11:14.305
Thank you.
[handset clicks]

11:14.341 --> 11:16.508
- [hands tap]
I owe you, mary.

11:16.643 --> 11:18.109
'course, I won't be able
to pay you

11:18.145 --> 11:20.311
