And they're gonna call back
tomorrow.

11:29.388 --> 11:31.256
- Sweet jesus!

11:31.391 --> 11:33.291
What am I gonna do?
- Oh!

11:33.360 --> 11:36.861
Well, I for one,
cannot wait to find out.

11:36.996 --> 11:38.996
[handset rattles roughly]
- ugh.

11:39.032 --> 11:41.132
Uh... Uh...

11:41.201 --> 11:43.201
I mean, I... I have an idea,

11:43.203 --> 11:45.870
Because you know how much
elizabeth loved you.

11:46.005 --> 11:47.539
- Yes.

11:47.541 --> 11:50.675
- I mean, she told me many
times you were her favourite.

11:50.677 --> 11:53.544
- Mm-hmm.
- I mean, really loved you.

11:54.881 --> 11:57.281
So perhaps... I mean...

11:57.317 --> 12:00.318
I think you'll agree to this,
